OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1774617128
OL,3,CSurvivor UK winner saves four
OL,4,Cpensioners stranded in floodwater
OL,6,FThe winner of Survivor UK sprang into
OL,7,Faction to save four pensioners after
OL,8,Fspotting a car stranded in rising
OL,9,Ffloodwater.
OL,11,FMatthew Haywood from Workington saw
OL,12,Ffour older people trapped inside a
OL,13,Ffloating Skoda Citigo on Tuesday March
OL,14,F24 in Seaton, Workington.
OL,16,FMatthew and his brother Harrison waded
OL,17,Fthrough the waist-high water to push
OL,18,Fthe car to safety, as other nearby
OL,19,Flocals rushed to help or record the
OL,20,Fscene on their phones.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
