FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1774617128
OL,3,CSurvivor UK winner saves four
OL,4,Cpensioners stranded in floodwater
OL,6,FMatthew said: "I'd seen there were
OL,7,Fpeople stuck floating in a car and I
OL,8,Fjust thought, I can't stand and watch
OL,9,Fthat.
OL,11,F"I knew I had to do something fast. I
OL,12,Fjumped in and started pulling it,
OL,13,Ftrying to get it to safety. Then more
OL,14,Flads came and helped and we managed to
OL,15,Fget it out.
OL,17,F"There was four elderly people in the
OL,18,Fcar and it was scary how quickly it
OL,19,Fwas getting worse."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
