FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1774617128
OL,3,CSurvivor UK winner saves four
OL,4,Cpensioners stranded in floodwater
OL,6,FHarrison Haywood got involved with the
OL,7,Frescue despite having recently had
OL,8,Fback surgery - he and Matthew were in
OL,9,Ffact on their way to pick up
OL,10,Fantibiotics when they spotted the
OL,11,Ffloating car.
OL,13,FHarrison told ITV Border: "I had
OL,14,Fsurgery on my very lower back, so I
OL,15,Fwas like, 'God, I can't be getting
OL,16,Finto this water.'
OL,18,F"As soon as my brother got in... I was
OL,19,Flike, 'I'm going into help him.'
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1774617128
OL,3,CSurvivor UK winner saves four
OL,4,Cpensioners stranded in floodwater
OL,6,F"I was thinking, if that was my gran
OL,7,Fand granda, I would want them out."
OL,9,FAlthough Matthew and his brother made
OL,10,Fthe rescue look easy, it was not all
OL,11,Fplain sailing, especially when the car
OL,12,Fbegan to touch soil.
OL,14,FMatthew told ITV Border: "We realised
OL,15,Fthey still had the handbrake on, so we
OL,16,Fcouldn't push it!
OL,18,F"We were like, 'please, handbrake off!'
OL,20,F"Then they took it off and we got the
OL,21,Fcar to shore eventually."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
