PN,35505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1774617128
OL,3,CSurvivor UK winner saves four
OL,4,Cpensioners stranded in floodwater
OL,6,FThe youngest ever winner of Survivor
OL,7,Fis no stranger to adversity, having
OL,8,Fwon the TV show in which contestants
OL,9,Fare dropped on a desert island and
OL,10,Fleft to fend for themselves, but he
OL,11,Fperhaps did not expect action so close
OL,12,Fto home.
OL,14,FHe said: "I love an adventure, but
OL,15,Fthis wasn't about that, it just shows
OL,16,Fhow important community is and how
OL,17,Fpeople come together when it matters.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1774617128
OL,3,CSurvivor UK winner saves four
OL,4,Cpensioners stranded in floodwater
OL,6,F"We are in an isolated part of the
OL,7,Fworld, so I think community spirit is
OL,8,Fimportant... looking after your
OL,9,Ffriends, and strangers as well."
OL,11,FA video of the rescue uploaded on
OL,12,Fsocial media has since amassed over
OL,13,F1.6 thousand 'likes'.
OL,15,FOver two hundred comments praised
OL,16,FMatthew's actions, while one simply
OL,17,Fsaid: "Told you it rained a lot
OL,18,Fyesterday!"
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/7
